Issue #11 — Anti-no-op revert demo
===================================

All of the change shipped by this PR (PR template update, Implementer/Reviewer
prompt updates, Adversarial Reviewer prompt, CI workflow, test runner, tests,
DESIGN.md update, evidence directory) has been removed via:
    git stash --include-untracked

Captured below is what happens when the PR's own test suite is invoked
against this pre-change state. The failures prove the change is doing work.

