tools/run_tests.sh does not exist in this state. The CI workflow
(.github/workflows/maestro-ci.yml) would fail at the 'Run tests' step
because it tries to execute a missing script:

bash: tools/run_tests.sh: No such file or directory
[bash exit 127]

